{"_response_info":{"status":"ok"},"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/heart-murmurs-and-driving.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/heart-murmurs-and-driving","title":"Heart murmurs and driving","format":"answer","updated_at":"2012-10-22T15:15:44+00:00","details":{"need_id":"2292","business_proposition":false,"description":"You may need to tell DVLA if you have a heart murmur - download the correct form if you need to let them know","language":"en","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>You may need to tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> if you have a heart murmur.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Car or motorcycle licence</h2>\n\n<p>You don&rsquo;t need to tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. You should stop driving for at least 1 month and only start driving again when you doctor tells you that you are safe to do so. For further information please download the leaflet &lsquo;CLE1066&rsquo;.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_192828.pdf\" title=\"Download leaflet 'CLE1066: Car or motorcycle drivers with heart conditions' (PDF, 176K)\" rel=\"external\">Download &lsquo;CLE1066 - Car or motorcycle drivers with heart conditions&rsquo; (PDF, 176K)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Bus, coach or lorry licence</h2>\n\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. Fill in form VOCH1 and send it to <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. The address is on the form. </p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_065302.pdf\" title=\"Download medical questionnaire\" rel=\"external\">Download &lsquo;VOCH1 - Confidential medical information questionnaire&rsquo; (PDF, 394KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n","alternative_title":"Driving with a heart murmur"},"tags":[],"related":[{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/driving-if-disabled.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/driving-if-disabled","title":"Medical conditions, disabilities and driving","format":"guide","updated_at":"2012-11-14T12:25:08+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/health-conditions-and-driving.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/health-conditions-and-driving","title":"Health conditions and driving","format":"answer","updated_at":"2013-01-08T10:36:08+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/giving-up-your-driving-licence.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/giving-up-your-driving-licence","title":"Surrendering your driving licence","format":"answer","updated_at":"2012-11-14T12:45:33+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/reapply-driving-licence-medical-condition.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/reapply-driving-licence-medical-condition","title":"Re-apply for a driving licence following a medical condition","format":"answer","updated_at":"2012-11-30T12:27:11+00:00"}]}